title: Brain Quest: AdelaideVisual Studio 2015 + ASP.NET 5 + DevOps
thumbnailDescription: Brain Quest Adelaide - Visual Studio 2015 + ASP.NET 5 + DevOps
eventShortDescription:
​This half day training course brings developers up-to-speed on the new features and benefits of Visual Studio 2015, ASP.NET vNext, and DevOps.

With detailed insight into project management, requirements gathering, user stories, testing, workflow, document managemet and Office integration, attendees will leave with a strong understanding of how to embrace Visual Studio 2015, ASP.NET 5 and DevOps in their organization.
